'''economy''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

Sets the economic condition for a new map.<br><br>
0 = steady - smaller, more frequent changes<br>
1 = fluctuating {default} - larger, less frequent changes<br>

<pre>
[difficulty]
economy = 0
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ 0 | 1 ]

'''Default:''' 1


